  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      Conduct a KAP survey before and after intervention and describe the current knowledge,
      attitudes and behaviors on drink driving in public and analyse the influential factors to
      provide rational strategies to enhance the awareness on drink driving in public.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
